{"tid":933734,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解得我放唔低？","createTime":"2018-12-08T17:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T18:40:22.000Z","uid":173326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9886a2753da731dec6f7bf438c04f29d4c1f07","tid":933734,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"個個都話時間沖淡一切/搵第二個就可以忘記上一個，但係我已經差唔多9年忘記唔到，中間試過考慮下溝其他吸引到我嘅女仔，但係我即刻諗起佢，跟住好內疚咁放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢當時明明都好傷心，點解佢可以放低我，好快識完一個又一個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解好多人都可以放低去識下個，我唔得，係咪我個delete/backspace制壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢同我都係無法放低過去嘅人就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992ed43f2da408c0302eb99cf4767e3803669fa6","tid":933734,"uid":73509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"我3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18ed721419156805f0c74afff6f7a37637bc029","tid":933734,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"992ed43f2da408c0302eb99cf4767e3803669fa6","tid":933734,"uid":73509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"我3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:30:08.000Z","msg":"拍左好耐拖？定初戀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defef204574ce2ca2b046e62bebab661f9078487","tid":933734,"uid":182110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"放得愈多心機 就愈難抽離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf243fec1ab17c67df46a648ffedbea40f6c5328","tid":933734,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"defef204574ce2ca2b046e62bebab661f9078487","tid":933734,"uid":182110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"r